quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,178,"Soni mwatundumalilani kwa kandaŵi kannono."
  37,179,"Soni gambagani kwalola; basi sampano taione."
  37,180,"Aŵambalene kusyene Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), Ambuje ŵamachili gakupunda ku yaakwasimba nayo (achimakafili)."
  43,67,"Asyoŵe lyele lisikulyo tachiŵengana ŵane ni ŵane, ikaŵeje ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah)."
  43,68,"(Ichiŵechetedwa ku ŵakulupilila kuti): E achikapolo Ŵangu! Ngam’ba ni woga lelo, soni jenumanja ngan’dandaula."
  43,69,"Aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile ma Ȃya Getu ni kuŵa Asilamu."
  44,52,"Ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo, ni achitutumule."
  44,53,"Takawaleje (nguwo sya) silika jwakuŵeŵela ni silika jwakandapalila, (ali atemi) mwakulolegana."
  44,54,"Mwele (ni muyichiŵela), ni tuchalombekasya ni achimmasyeto ŵameso gakulanguka soni gekulungwa mwakusalalila."
  46,31,"“E majini gajetu! Mun’jitikani nkuŵilanga jwa Allah (Muhammadi ﷺ), ni munkulupilile jwalakwe, (Allah) tankululuchile sambi syenu, ni tam’bambasye ku ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope.”"
  46,32,"“Sano jwatatende ngan’jitika nkuŵilanga jwa Allah; nikuti nganijuŵa junnepelekasyisye (Allah kumpa ipotesi) pa chilambo, soni nganijukola jwalakwe jwangaŵaga Allah akun’gosa ŵaliose. Ŵanganyao ali nkupotela kwakuonechela.”"
  46,33,"Ana ngaakuiona yanti Allah Ajula juŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka ni nganijupela pakuigumba yalakweyo, kuti juŵele Jwakombola kwajimusya ŵawe? Elo, chisimu Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose juŵele Jwakombola."
  47,22,"Mwinetu jenumanja patin’galauche (kuleka chikulupi ni kuleka kumenyana ngondo ni makafili), tim’be nkuwatanganya pachilambo nikataga ulongo wenu (mwamwatendelaga kala ndema jaujinga)."
  47,23,"Ŵanganyao ni aŵala ŵaŵalwesile Allah, niŵatesile kuŵa ŵangapikana, ni kugatenda kuŵa gangalola meso gao."
  47,24,"Ana ngaakujichetelela Qur’an, kapena m’mitima mwao mwana achinampatiika ŵakwe (mwanti ni jiwugalidwe kwangajipikana Qur’anijo)?"
  48,13,"Sano jwangaakunkulupilila Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, basi chisimu Uwwe tugalinganyichisye makafili Moto Wakulapuka."
  48,14,"Soni Allah ni Nsyene uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, akunkululuchilaga jwansachile, ni kumpa ilagasyo jwansachile, ni aŵele Allah Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope."
  48,15,"Taŵechete akusigalila munyuma pandema jatim’bigule kuja kuchipanje chakupalagula (cha ku Khaibara) kuti nkachijigale: “Tulekaani tunkuuye.” Akusaka agalawusye maloŵe ga Allah. Jilani: “Nganim’ba ntukuyiye. Mwele ni muŵaŵechetele kalape Allah.” Basi ŵanganyao tajile: “(Ngwamba), nambo nkututendela litima.” (Ngwamba), nambo aŵele akakumanyilila ikaŵeje panandipe."
  49,1,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ngasinnongolela (kupeleka nganisyo syenu) pameso pa Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, ni mun’jogopeje Allah, chisimu Allah ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope."
  49,2,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ngasinnyakulaga maloŵe genu pachanya pa liloŵe lya Ntume ﷺ, nambo soni ngasimunnyanyichilaga jwalakwe liloŵe yankuti pakunyanyichilana ŵane kwa ŵane, gatakwika mugajonasiche masengo genu kutendaga jenumanja nkakumanyilila."
  49,3,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakutondoya maloŵe gao kwa Ntenga jwa Allah ﷺ, ŵanganyao ni aŵala ŵaajilinjile Allah mitima jao pa woga (wakun’jogopa Jwalakwe), akwete kupata ŵanganyao chikululuko ni malipilo gamakulungwa nnope."